Personal Bio Website

This is a simple and responsive Personal Bio Website built using HTML and CSS.  
The project showcases my basic frontend skills and introduces who I am as an aspiring software developer.

 Features

- Clean and modern UI  
- Smooth animations (slide-in, glow effects)  
- Responsive layout with flexible sections  
- Profile image section with rounded design  
- About Me section with highlighted keywords  
- Experience counters  
- Footer with social media icons  
- Fully styled using custom CSS  
- Font Awesome icons integrated

Technologies Used
- HTML5  
- CSS3 
- Font Awesome Icons  

 Folder Structure
│── index.html
│── style.css
│── /images
│ └── xav.png

How to Run the Project
1. Download or clone the repository:
2. Open the folder.
3. Double-click "index.html" to open it in your browser.

That’s it!


